Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really no need to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that field of pampas grass a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I'm holding her like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but we didn't end up like this in the way that you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I gave alcohol to an innocent girl and took her to a secluded place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I deeply apologise for doing such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't aware of the details, so I became a little upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that a little, you violent intimidator?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apologise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamio,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face looks familiar, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't stand out very much, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are acquainted though,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,since you've been here a few times to receive check-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, weird things really did happen on your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But that just makes it all the more memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you make friends with Kano instead of just playing with me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you might get along pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're both pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to pick up today's salary for my part-time work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be evasive if I try to pick it up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, part-time sala...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already gone to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to turn on lights so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't properly check up on you in the dark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Kano, you've matured a lot too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me in weird places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a proper clinical technique known as "examination by touch."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In examination tests, you don't caress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a weird sound just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess it was just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But we don't keep cats at our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I must be hearing things then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Kano, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong, Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Has it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Always, always, repeating the same words!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl... my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,my one treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my precious sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Onee-chan hugging me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You were falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You came and hugged me, so I held you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I've been telling you to hurry up and sleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But can we be like this for a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You did this for me when Daddy died, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a nice smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, the cicadas came in from the ventilation fan again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, the soy sauce container fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, the salad oil spilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, Yukito-san's bacon egg turned out horribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, something happened to this food, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those "oi, he's actually eating it" eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes aren't like that, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:06:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't taste like cicadas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of... Various things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At least work your salary's worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through everything once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I have something else for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to say something, why don't you just say it clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I won't agree to a salary increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's about last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.26,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't seen him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've been looking for him for a while, but I can't seem to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato, come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato... where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's starting to set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We've ran out of places to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you search with your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that my magic is for different things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told when I was given this bandanna
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep it on until I became an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it off until then, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did that, I'd be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you get it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was small, so I don't remember very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but this has been wrapped around my wrist ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been troublesome at times, especially during swimming and body check-ups, and I was even bullied a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Onee-chan always saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we've been able to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finally arrived at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, there's no way he'd be in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realised where Potato is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:16.72,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, don't ever make me worry like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But why were you in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yukito-kun, how did you know that he was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... well... um... what do you call it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko pikopik...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...a kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Potato, from now on, you can't disappear without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pity that you don't behave as well as you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really not remember anything about what happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-kun, will you listen to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll listen to anything you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly remember anything about my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, her body wasn't very strong from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She became sick right after she gave birth to me and passed away when I was about 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad would often say, "Your mum was like you."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I couldn't imagine her very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not so bad; I wasn't very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan became a substitute for my mum, and dad was always around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means that Onee-chan was without a mum for a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, I've thought that that wasn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad was always busy managing the clinic, and his health collapsed from working too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing is happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan works and cares for me, but I can't do anything to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not of much help either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could use magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,would use it to meet my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet her and apologise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...for many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You should thank her, not apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is the reason that you're here right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone told me, "I'm sorry that you gave birth to me,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your mum, Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been where your mum is for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My mum was looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"On the other side of this sky, there is a girl with wings."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my mum's favourite saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for that girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someday, if I'm able to fly in the sky, I'll search for that girl for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\bord0\c&H000000&\pos(640,70)}Kamio
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl is in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't feeling very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so she's sleeping alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were there, she'd only become more conscientious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for a child to be conscientious of her parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many factors, even though I'm her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you aren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that I couldn't pick you up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're busy with many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like dinosaurs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she like dinosaurs so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been like that since she was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything about her even though she's your own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget that yesterday was her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, does that girl act strangely during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she always strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if there's nothing, then it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, enough with this trivial talk; it's finally today's main event:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Erotic Confessions Corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.93,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,How did we end up going there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm starting to get hot just by saying the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a pervert or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because dinosaurs flourished for a long time, but then faced their end, extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of sad and makes my heart palpitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have those dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In my dreams, I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to describe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the smell of the wind, the breeze caressing my skin, the flow of air, and the passing of the seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that I'm going back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of a dream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where my dream is taking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please try not to get hit by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the suika wari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, at Kano's behest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you spoiling her a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Set...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible to make money here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't body bash me every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We waited for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi seemed sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop acting so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was a little busy yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As punishment, you'll live here from today on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.74,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you want me to leave this town in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstance was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It stood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san, you have such a wonderful special talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Clap clap clap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use a bit of what is called "magic."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is full of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, a special thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:56.88,Note,,0,0,0,,[Ticket: Usable Worldwide, Rice Ticket, 1000 Yen]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl with wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm searching for the girl that my mum sought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child, there was a picture book like that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside that picture book, there was a girl with pure white wings on her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I, with a childish heart, wanted to fly into the sky with her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing strange about you, even if the purpose of your journey is to search for that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone has a different destination in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars will probably be pretty tonight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it well at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come right now, Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A destination, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Done with today's homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,C-A-R-D-S.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to play cards with you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we have come from a faraway planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:54.48,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Mizuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not at the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've searched the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that way to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, do you have any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. Let's just search where we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:20.96,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Kirishima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pi-ka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he asking us to follow him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But she said that she searched...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.65,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Tightly clasping my only treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,by my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing this because I think that you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally decided to go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that if I do that, everyone can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I can meet the girl you're searching for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:24:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when it'll be,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll definitely bring that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be grateful if you can help my sister until I return.
